Implementing a home-based exercise program for patients with advanced, incurable 
diseases after discharge and their caregivers: lessons we have learned.

Siemens W(1), Wehrle A(2), Gaertner J(3), Henke M(4), Deibert P(5), Becker G(6).

Author information:
(1)Department of Palliative Care, University Medical Center Freiburg, 
Robert-Koch-Straße 3, 79106, Freiburg, Germany. 
waldemar.siemens@uniklinik-freiburg.de.
(2)Department of Internal Medicine, Institute for Exercise- and Occupational 
Medicine, University Medical Center Freiburg, Hugstetter Str. 49, 79106, 
Freiburg, Germany. anja.wehrle@uniklinik-freiburg.de.
(3)Department of Palliative Care, University Medical Center Freiburg, 
Robert-Koch-Straße 3, 79106, Freiburg, Germany. 
jan.gaertner@uniklinik-freiburg.de.
(4)Department of Radiation Oncology, University Medical Center Freiburg, 
Robert-Koch-Straße 3, 79106, Freiburg, Germany. 
michael.henke@uniklinik-freiburg.de.
(5)Department of Internal Medicine, Institute for Exercise- and Occupational 
