Risk of Major Cardiovascular Events in People with Down Syndrome.

Sobey CG(1), Judkins CP(2), Sundararajan V(3), Phan TG(4), Drummond GR(1), 
Srikanth VK(5).

Author information:
(1)Cardiovacular Disease Program, Biomedicine Discovery Institute and Department 
of Pharmacology, Monash University, Clayton, Victoria, Australia; Department of 
Surgery, Monash Medical Centre, Southern Clinical School, Monash University, 
Clayton, Victoria, Australia.
(2)Cardiovacular Disease Program, Biomedicine Discovery Institute and Department 
